quran[67]{c,v,t}:
  90,1,Nguulumbila awu musi (wa Maaka)
  90,2,Soni mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) tinchiŵa ŵakundisyidwa (kuputa ngondo) mu wele musiwu
  90,3,Ni ngullumbila soni nangolo ni uŵelesi wajuŵeleche
  90,4,Chisimu pamasile patun'gumbile mundu m’matabu
  90,5,Ana juganichisya yanti pangali ŵampaka ankombole (kumpa ilagasyo)
  90,6,"Jukuŵecheta (mwakutwanga kuti): “Njonasile yipanje yejinji (kuti Usilamu usilale).”"
  90,7,Ana juganichisya kuti pangali ŵaakun'bona
  90,8,Ana nganitun'gumbila meso gaŵili (gajukulolela)
  90,9,Ni lulimi kwisa soni ngomo siŵili (syajukuŵechetela)
  90,10,"Ni tun’jongolele matala gaŵili (lyambone ni lyakusakala, kuti jusagule lyajukusaka)"
  90,11,Ana pakwete pajujesile litala lyamwitumbi (lyalikam’bikasye ku Mbepo)
  90,12,Ana ni chichi champaka chimmanyisye ya litala lyamwitumbi
  90,13,"(Litala lyamwitumbi nimasengo gambone nambo gakunonopa, mpela): gopola kapolo"
  90,14,Kapena kupeleka yakulya palisiku lyasala
  90,15,(Kumpa) jwawina jwapaulongo
  90,16,Kapena masikini jwaluwunduwundupe (ligongo lyakulaga nnope)
  90,17,"Soni nikuŵa (nkutola yakulyajo) jumpepe mwa aŵala ŵaakulupilile, ni kulimbikasyanaga ya kupilila soni ni kulimbikasyanaga ya kutendelana chanasa"
  90,18,Ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵakun'dyo (ŵali ŵambone)
  90,19,Nambo ŵandu ŵaagakaaniile ma Ȃya Getu ŵanganyao niŵandu ŵakunchiji (ŵali ŵakusakala)
  90,20,Kwaŵanganyao kuchiŵa kwana Moto Wakuunichila ni kutika (wangali pakopochela)
  91,1,Ngulilumbila lyuŵa ni lilanguka lyakwe
  91,2,Ni mwesi ndema jaukulikuya (lyuŵalyo)
  91,3,Ni muusi ndema jaukulilosya palangulangu
  91,4,Ni chilo ndema jachikuliunichila (kuti likaoneka)
  91,5,Kwisa soni liwunde ni Juŵalitaŵile (mwakulitalichisya)
  91,6,Ni litaka ni Juŵalitandiche (mwakulijaasasya)
  91,7,Kwisa soni ntima ni Juŵaukolosisye
  91,8,Basi ni jwaumanyisye yakusakala yakwe ni yambone yakwe
  91,9,Pamasile paapundile jwauswejesye (ntima wakwe)
  91,10,Soni pamasile papelelwe jwautwinyichisye (ntima wakwe mu sambi)
  91,11,Ŵaakaaniile ŵanya Asamudu ligongo lyakusumba mpika kwao
  91,12,Ndema jajwalipeleche jwakusakalilwa jwao (kuulaga ngamiya)
  91,13,"Basi Ntenga jwa Allah (Swaleh) ŵasalile kuti: “(Aji ni) ngamiya ja Allah, sano ngasin'jikanyaga kumwa mesi (palisiku lyakwe)"
  91,14,Nambo ŵankaaniile nikujiulaga; basi Ambuje ŵao ŵajonasile ligongo lya chileŵi chao; niŵalandenye pachonasikocho
  91,15,Soni jwangajogopa yakuichisya yakwe
  92,1,Nguchilumbila chilo ndema jachikuunichila (chilichose ni chipi chakwe)
  92,2,Ni muusi ndema jakukulanguka
  92,3,Ni Ajula (Allah) Jwagumbile chachilume ni chachikongwe
  92,4,Chisimu itendo yenu iŵele yakulekangana-lekangana
  92,5,Sano mundu jwaakutola (petala lya Allah) ni kuŵa niwoga (wakun'jogopa Jwalakwe)
  92,6,Ni kulupilila yambone nnope (yatakalipidwe ligongo lyakutola)
  92,7,Basi chitun'jepepachisye litala lyakwalukangana (lyakutendela yambone)
  92,8,Nambo mundu jwachatende ubayili ni kuliona kusichila
  92,9,Ni kanila yambone nnope (yaakajiile kuipata akatole)
  92,10,Basi chitun'jepepachisye litala lyausito (lyakutendela yakusakala)
  92,11,Soni ngasichija kunkamuchisya chipanje chakwe ndema jagwila (ku Moto)
  92,12,Chisimu Kukwetu nikwachili chongolo
  92,13,Soni chisimu Uwwe ni twachinsyene Akhera ni Duniya
  92,14,Basi nguntetela ya Moto waukolela (mwamachili)
  92,15,Ngaaja kuwujinjila ikaŵeje jwakusakalilwa nnope
  92,16,Ajula jwaakuŵa nkukanila ni kusyulula
  92,17,Ni takaŵambasyidwe nao mundu jwawoga kusyene (wakun'jogopa Allah)
  92,18,Ajula jwaakutola chipanje chakwe pakuliswejesya
  92,19,Soni pangali kwa jwalakwe jwalijose jwaŵantendele yaukoto yaikuŵa ili nkuusyidwa
  92,20,Ikaŵeje (jukutola) pakusachilila Ngope ja M’mbujeegwe (Allah) Jwapenani kusyene (kuti jukajione ku Akhera)
  92,21,Ni juchija kusengwa
  93,1,Nguulumbila nsana
  93,2,Ni chilo ndema jachikutulala
  93,3,Ngananneka Ambuje ŵenu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) soni nganam'benga
  93,4,Soni chisimu umi wambesi uŵele wambone nnope kukwenu kupunda wandanda
  93,5,Soni tachija kumpa Ambuje ŵenu (yambone) ni tinchisengwa
  93,6,Ana nganansimana n'di ŵawina nikumpa liwuto lyambone
  93,7,Soni ni ŵansimene n'di ŵangachimanya chongoko (jajili Qur'an ni malamusi ga Dini) nikun'jongola
  93,8,Ni ŵansimene soni n'di ŵakulaga nikunsichilisya
  93,9,Sano mwanache jwawina basi ngasimunchima
  93,10,Nombe soni jwakuŵenda basi ngasimunkalipila
  93,11,Soni chindimba cha Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) basi chisimbani (pakutogolela ni kutenda yambone)